---
title: Easy BBQ Chicken & Bacon Pizza with Cheddar Cheese & Rocket Salad
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up with smokey BBQ chicken and bacon and crunchy sweetcorn pizza. Oozing with Cheddar cheese and smattered with rocket leaves for a peppery kick, you can pile this on your plate in less than 30 minutes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-bbq-chicken-bacon-pizza-5be9b600.jpg
